-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">“软件</strong>”之间的复杂关系。</p> \n<p _msttexthash=\"289423953\" _msthash=\"817\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong _istranslated=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">关键词</strong>： 运动中的视觉—熟练的运动—板球击球—视觉训练—扫视—双眼视觉。</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"12289277\" _msthash=\"816\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">知觉机制</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p _msttexthash=\"996110141\" _msthash=\"815\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">这种机制从受体接收信息，例如视网膜接收视觉信息，从内耳接收平衡信息。知觉机制重新组织和解释信息。信息的选择可能会受到运动员以前的经历的影响。</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"11014783\" _msthash=\"814\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">决策机制</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p _msttexthash=\"803248485\" _msthash=\"813\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">来自感知机制的信息被传递到决策机制，决策机制决定适当的行动。该机制与响应选择和策略形成有关。这也可能受到运动员以前经验的影响。</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"14954147\" _msthash=\"812\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">执行器机制</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p _msttexthash=\"2658260150\" _msthash=\"811\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">如果决策机构选择电机响应，则相关信息将传递到效应机构，该机构控制和组织所需运动的顺序。神经命令从中枢神经系统传递到运动所需的肌肉群。通过反馈，这种机制可以在执行过程中控制移动，并以某种方式评估最终结果，从而允许将来进行更改。</p> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"4907604\" _msthash=\"810\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">硬件</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p _msttexthash=\"1653656550\" _msthash=\"809\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">第一种类型的视觉信息处理涉及视觉信息的接收;这受运动员视觉系统的眼部特征的影响。视觉系统的硬件组件可以使用验光和正视测试进行测量，并构成运动视力检查的基础，例如静态视力测量。</p> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"5443685\" _msthash=\"808\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">软件</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p _msttexthash=\"2737058623\" _msthash=\"807\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">第二种类型的视觉信息处理涉及对视觉信息的感知，该感知受运动员通过经验制定的策略的影响，从而更有效地处理传入的信息。运动视觉的软件方面包括信息处理策略、从记忆中编码和检索感知信息、从提前提示和球飞行提示中提取相关信息，以及预期技能的使用。</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" _msttexthash=\"6083610\" _msthash=\"806\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">回顾</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p _msttexthash=\"3655109185\" _msthash=\"805\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">使用<strong _istranslated